Quote:  <i>kauri</i> also <i>kaurie</i> or <i>kaury</i> or <i>kawrie</i> or <i>kawry or <i>cowrie</i> or <i>kaori, n</i>, pl <i>kauris</i> also <i>kauries</i> [Maori <i>kawri</i>] or <i>kauri pine</i> : a tree of the genus <i>Agathis</i>; esp : a tall

